perhaps the technological development of China's aerospace

578
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:28,050
will be completely different.

579
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:29,760
But I believe

580
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:32,180
no matter how far it develops,

581
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:34,680
our purpose and meaning

582
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:37,720
should remain the same as in the beginning.

583
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:39,320
I hope that by then,

584
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:42,850
I will still be fighting on the front lines of aerospace.

585
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,120
You will always be my role model.

586
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,080
That's right.

587
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:50,180
No matter where we are,

588
00:38:51,160 --> 00:38:54,200
the brightest star in the sky will always be you.

589
00:38:55,200 --> 00:38:55,960
Mr. Qin.

590
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:58,440
I know

591
00:38:58,440 --> 00:38:59,840
you've always been here.

592
00:39:00,120 --> 00:39:00,880
Mr. Qin.

593
00:39:02,240 --> 00:39:03,040
Rest assured.

594
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:05,040
We've taken the baton.

595
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:08,250
We will continue to move forward step by step.

596
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,880
Now it's the moon,

597
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,460
and next it's Mars.

598
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:14,040
There will be even more distant places

599
00:39:14,240 --> 00:39:15,970
where we leave our footprints.

600
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:18,450
Along with our Five-Starred Red Flag.

601
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:21,280
We will keep working hard.

602
00:39:29,520 --> 00:39:30,400
That's enough.

603
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:53,400
Let's go.

604
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,160
Mr. Qin.

605
00:39:56,360 --> 00:39:58,800
I understand your question.

606
00:39:59,600 --> 00:40:00,320
Now,

607
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:02,600
I have the answer.

608
00:40:15,240 --> 00:40:16,680
In the vast universe,

609
00:40:17,600 --> 00:40:19,860
I feel we are all just tiny grains of dust.

610
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:23,400
Whether meeting or flying apart,

611
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:26,580
it is an entanglement of gravitational orbits.

612
00:40:28,680 --> 00:40:29,680
Earth

613
00:40:29,680 --> 00:40:31,740
is the cradle of human civilization.

614
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:35,410
But humanity is unwilling to live in the cradle forever.

615
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:39,400
Exploring space and embracing the universe.

616
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,220
In the unknown deep space,

617
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:43,360
lies the future of humanity.

618
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:48,330
Chinese civilization,

619
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:49,600
as one of the oldest

620
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:51,330
civilizations on this planet,

621
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,920
is radiating new vitality.

622
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:59,290
A generation of young Chinese astronauts

623
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:00,680
are full of ambition

624
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:02,400
and ready to set sail.

625
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,960
This will be a long journey across hundreds of millions,

626
00:41:05,960 --> 00:41:07,800
or even billions of light-years in distance,

627
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:08,760
spanning thousands

628
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:11,000
or tens of thousands of years.

629
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:14,200
A human's life,

630
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:16,120
in comparison,

631
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:18,080
is merely a brief moment.

632
00:41:19,520 --> 00:41:20,480
Our journey

633
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:22,760
is the sea of stars.

634
00:41:23,680 --> 00:41:24,600
But life

635
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:26,600
is endless.

636
00:42:31,040 --> 00:42:32,520
Towards the sea of stars,

637
00:42:33,160 --> 00:42:33,960
let's set off.

638
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:03,600
The names of spacecraft and related missions in this drama have been fictionalized.

